omega_arag_method: Calculated using PyCO2SYS version 1.8.3. measurements_from: All environmental metadata measurements reported for this sample were taken from the bottle data file. omega_arag and omega_calc were calculated using PyCO2Sys version 1.8.3 with two input parameters given in the following priority based on the availability of data: 1) diss_inorg_carb and tot_alkalinity, 2) diss_inorg_carb and pH, and 3) tot_alkalinity and pH. The following optional nutrients were included in PyCO2Sys calculations for omega_arag and omega_calc if data is available: salinity, temp, pressure, silicate, and phosphate.
